     <div class="mainleftcon"> 
      <div class="mainleft_title"> 
       <h1> 可怕！还敢在朋友圈晒自拍吗 ？看看这个年轻女教师遭遇了什么… </h1> 
      </div> 
      <div class="mainleft_two"> 
       <div class="mainleft_from">
         作者：
        <a href="http://toutiao.weiyoubaba.com/m1646/">明智家庭教育</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; 发布时间：2016-08-27
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="mainleft_three"> 
       <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-type="gif" data-ratio="0.11875" data-w="640" width="auto" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/e6u8Up4CWsoUyMWWC4bicJsdUSYNTziatpMJ5RURvicK1oRvcIwE8icAiaA8ciaplicVic8kwSTFdrOj0AmO4KUwHrme4A/0?wx_fmt=gif" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" /><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p class="" style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 28pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 13.5pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-size:auto; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); line-height: 24.381px; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">近日，在广州市白云区从事教育工作的李小姐发现，自己的照片被人在网上随意发布，并放在了一些涉嫌有色情内容的宣传海报上！她感到非常气愤，而原因很可能与她发布在微信朋友圈的自拍照有关。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img width="auto" title="1467950488607608.jpg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.6734375" data-w="640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/l8OScYWXQkUA6jV07x8K7acKytXFQpGy73cJjH73rH95F7U3TDuOuiaYvChY5nFfEdicg5XSHLNf6MibSCjkviaK6w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">今年24岁的李小姐（化名）在广州白云区新市工作，是一名教师，6月21日晚上11点多，她突然收到朋友发来的信息，称看到她的自拍照出现在网上。</p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img width="auto" title="1467950490542329.jpg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.6734375" data-w="640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/l8OScYWXQkUA6jV07x8K7acKytXFQpGyEHWIdYk3yJ0ewc41xk3T4JR7ibumcLkMELjyJIXqPVKYA8XFyjBTn7A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">对此，李小姐非常吃惊，并要求朋友发截图给她，只见一个名字为“俏金莲”的用户发布多张女子的自拍照，而其中一张则是李小姐本人，该照片上印有“中外高档兼职、美女、上酒店宾馆”等字样，底下还留有一个手机号码。</p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img width="auto" title="1467958953940029.jpg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.6734375" data-w="640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/l8OScYWXQkUA6jV07x8K7acKytXFQpGyooAUdFrkEeIpQ1GhW73ic6yqS0QYXnzQicfdrTYvrnR96aZRloh8wKEQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">朋友拨打了这个电话，一名女子接电话说，可以安排上门服务，但不是照片上的女子，照片是网络图片。</p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">李小姐说，朋友当时是在广州火车站搜索“附近的人”弹出的广告，而到了23日早上，另外一位朋友又在其他地方搜索到同样的一条信息。李小姐感到十分气愤，自己作为一名教师，有正当职业，但现在无缘无故被人盗取了照片，并发在了这些广告中，对她个人声誉有造成了损害。</p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">李小姐介绍，这张自拍照是自己一个月前拍的，随后发布在个人的微信朋友圈上，而自己微信上的好友都是学生家长或者亲戚朋友，没想到发生这样的事。</p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">事后，李小姐已经报案，白云警方对此立案调查。</p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img width="auto" title="1467950490433200.jpg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.6734375" data-w="640" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/l8OScYWXQkUA6jV07x8K7acKytXFQpGyD0IucAAic8zQodnY9n3lwOKbnibs5Q0rkaoRPrHOM0h4yjd5M8013fAQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">对此，有律师表示，在这件事中，盗窃李小姐照片的人已经涉嫌侵犯其肖像权及名誉权。律师也提醒，如今，网络发达，市民在发布个人照片等信息时要注意保护好个人隐私。</p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p><p></p>
        <section data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
         <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
          <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
           <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-size:auto; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">说 关 键！</strong></span></p>
          </section>
          <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
           <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不少人喜欢在朋友圈上“晒”各类生活信息和照片。但你知道吗，这些行为间接泄露了个人的相关信息，如果被别有用心的人看到、利用，将造成家中个人财物被盗窃，甚至危害自己和家人人身安全。</p>
            <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
            <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">根据专业人士的研究，朋友圈越来越成了敏感信息泄露的“重灾区”。为了不成为黑客、骗子、小偷的“业务对象”，你在晒朋友圈的时候要控制、控制、再控制。</p>
           </section>
          </section>
         </section>
        </section><p></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p><p></p>
        <section data-source="bj.96weixin.com" style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
         <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
          <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
           <section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
            <section class="" style="margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
             <span class="" style="padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; border-radius: 0.5em; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 0.2em 0.2em 0.1em; font-size:auto; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(95, 156, 239); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(95, 156, 239);">
              <section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">
               <span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">朋友圈，这些东西尽量少晒</strong></span>
              </section></span>
             <section style="max-width: 100%; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section>
            </section>
            <p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
           </section>
          </section>
         </section>
